data.enText: an entertainer who performs difficult acts such as balancing on high ropes, especially at a circus

simple_means.memory_skill: acro 顶点，高点 + bat 打 → 在高处表演打斗 → 杂技演员

tr: an athlete who performs acts requiring skill and agility and coordination

value.def: An acrobat is an entertainer who performs difficult physical acts such as jumping and balancing, especially in a circus.

partsOfSpeech.dec: acro 顶点，高点 + bat 打 → 在高处表演打斗 → 杂技演员
acro 顶点，高点 + bat 打 + ics …术 → 杂技
acro 顶点，高点 +〔o〕nym 名字 → 名字的第一个〔字母〕→ 首字母缩略词
acro 顶点，高点 + phob 恐惧，厌恶 + ia 某种病 → 恐高症
acro 顶点，高点 + polis 城市 → 城市周围高高的城堡 → 卫城
partsOfSpeech.d: 卫城（古希腊城市设防的城堡或要塞）
